Class JobRecoveryTypeException

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class JobRecoveryTypeException
extends JobRecoveryException
    This exception is thrown when an attempted recover is performed using Ds3ClientHelpers and the JobRequestType of the specified job does not match the type of recovery to be performed. Ds3ClientHelpers.recoverReadJob(UUID) requires the specified job to be of type JobRequestType.GET. Ds3ClientHelpers.recoverWriteJob(UUID) requires the specified job to be of type JobRequestType.PUT.
